430Ôćĺ    /// where the hash-to-point is computed externally.
431Ôćĺ    ///
432Ôćĺ    /// # Arguments
433Ôćĺ    ///
434Ôćĺ    /// * `sk` - The secret key
435Ôćĺ    /// * `hash_point` - Pre-computed hash point (512 coefficients in [0, Q))
436Ôćĺ    /// * `seed` - 56-byte seed for the sampling PRNG
437Ôćĺ    ///
438Ôćĺ    /// # Returns
